OL,7,FWest Ham have sacked head coach Julen
OL,8,FLopetegui after less than eight months
OL,9,Fin charge.
OL,11,FThe Hammers are expected to announce
OL,12,Fformer Brighton and Chelsea boss
OL,13,FGraham Potter as the Spaniard's
OL,14,Freplacement in the next 24 hours.
OL,16,FTalks with Potter are reportedly at an
OL,17,Fadvanced stage on Tuesday night, with
OL,18,Fa few contract details still to be
OL,19,Fironed out.
