OL,7,FLopetegui took training as usual on
OL,8,FTuesday and reported for work on
OL,9,FWednesday to be officially told his
OL,10,Fspell in charge was over.
OL,12,F"West Ham United can confirm that head
OL,13,Fcoach Julen Lopetegui has today left
OL,14,Fthe club.
OL,16,F"The first half of the 2024/25 season
OL,17,Fhas not aligned with the club's
OL,18,Fambitions and the club has therefore
OL,19,Ftaken action in line with its
OL,20,Fobjectives.
