OL,7,FThe 58-year-old was appointed in May
OL,8,Fto replace David Moyes, who left the
OL,9,Fclub at the end of last season after
OL,10,Fhis contract expired.
OL,12,FHe was tasked with bringing a more
OL,13,Fattacking style of play to the London
OL,14,FStadium after some fans grew
OL,15,Ffrustrated with Moyes' pragmatic
OL,16,Fapproach, even though the Scot led the
OL,17,Fclub to a first trophy in 43 years
OL,18,Fwhen they won the Europa Conference
OL,19,FLeague in 2023.
