OL,7,FBut despite a #130million spending
OL,8,Fspree in the summer, bringing in nine
OL,9,Fplayers including Germany striker
OL,10,FNiclas Fullkrug and Wolves captain Max
OL,11,FKilman, results have been poor with
OL,12,FWest Ham a lowly 14th in the Premier
OL,13,FLeague.
OL,15,FLopetegui's position was under threat
OL,16,Fin early December following a 3-1
OL,17,Fdefeat at Leicester, but a run of four
OL,18,Fmatches unbeaten earned him a stay of
OL,19,Fexecution.
