OL,7,FHowever, the manner of the 5-0 home
OL,8,Fdefeat by Liverpool after Christmas,
OL,9,Ffollowed by a 4-1 loss at Manchester
OL,10,FCity on Saturday, set alarms bells
OL,11,Fringing again among the West Ham
OL,12,Fhierarchy.
OL,14,FTechnical director Tim Steidten, who
OL,15,Fis understood to have advocated
OL,16,Fappointing Potter in the summer, has
OL,17,Fbeen staying away from the training
OL,18,Fground amid reports of tension between
OL,19,Fhim and Lopetegui.
