OL,7,FWest Ham say the German, 45, is
OL,8,Ffocusing on the January transfer
OL,9,Fwindow, which opened last week.
OL,11,FThe club are looking at potential
OL,12,Fstriking options with Jarrod Bowen out
OL,13,Ffor six weeks with a fractured foot
OL,14,Fand Michail Antonio facing a long road
OL,15,Fback after he was injured in a car
OL,16,Faccident last month.
